lead_paragraph: Sergei Bobrovsky was flawless as the last line of defense. The Columbus Blue Jackets goalie had plenty of help up front on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Bobrovsky Stops 32 Shots, Blue Jackets Beat Stars 3-0
